    tags: ["sap","purchase orders","procurement","workflow","tutorial"],
    excerpt: "This comprehensive guide will teach you everything about Purchase Orders and Procurement Workflow in SAP. You'll learn about concepts, practical examples, and best practices to optimize your use of SAP for purchasing.",
