    tags: ["shutdown planning","engineering","tutorial","guidelines","beginners"],
    excerpt: "This guide provides a thorough understanding of shutdown planning for engineers, covering essential concepts, practical examples, and actionable steps to succeed. Learn the importance of shutdown planning and how to implement it effectively in your projects.",
