    excerpt: "This comprehensive guide delves into the Critical Path Method (CPM), providing actionable insights, real-world examples, and best practices for effective project management. Readers will learn about the intricacies of CPM, how to apply it, and common pitfalls to avoid.",
    sourceUrl: "",
