    tags: ["project management","forecasting","eac","etc","advanced techniques"],
    excerpt: "This comprehensive guide covers the advanced techniques of Project Forecasting using EAC and ETC methods. Readers will learn actionable insights, code examples, and best practices to enhance their forecasting capabilities.",
